creator: basant.kukreja@sun.com
text:
CustomLog Entry in httpd-vhosts.conf.in is defined as
CustomLog "@rel_logfiledir@/dummy-host.example.com-access_log common"

The correct format is :
CustomLog "@rel_logfiledir@/dummy-host.example.com-access_log" common

creator: basant.kukreja@sun.com

Patch for the bug
